author: NIKHIL SHARMA
description: A 17-year-old student was shot by a motorcyclist in Faridabad's Shyam Colony while returning from a library. The assailant fired a country-made pistol, hitting her shoulder and hand. Locals attempted to apprehend the fleeing attacker, who discarded his weapon. The girl is stable and receiving treatment. Police are investigating the motive and have identified a suspect.
title: Faridabad horror: 17-year-old girl shot by jilted lover; attack caught on cam

author: PRATYUSH RAJ
description: Twelve years after a nine-year-old Shafali Verma begged her father to take her to Lahli to see Sachin Tendulkar, the Rohtak girl returned the favour, gifting her idol a World Cup in his own backyard. With Tendulkar in the stands, Shafali’s bat and ball did the talking as life came full circle.
title: From Lahli to Navi Mumbai: Shafali Verma's return gift to idol Sachin

author: TOI WORLD DESK
description: Donald Trump threatened to withhold federal funds from New York City if Zohran Mamdani, whom he labeled a Communist, wins the mayoral election. Trump predicted economic disaster under Mamdani's leadership and urged New Yorkers to vote for former Governor Andrew Cuomo instead.
title: NYC mayoral race: Trump threatens to cut federal funds if Mamdani wins polls

author: TOI SPORTS DESK
description: Ravichandran Ashwin lauded young spinner Sree Charani for her exceptional World Cup performance. He believes Charani is a future superstar. Ashwin compared India's 2025 World Cup triumph to historic wins under Kapil Dev and MS Dhoni. He highlighted captain Harmanpreet Kaur's efforts in achieving this milestone. The team's success will be remembered for generations.
title: 'She’s the reason India won': Ashwin can’t stop praising India’s breakout bowler

author: H M CHAITHANYA SWAMY
description: A Bengaluru man, Naveen K Mon, was arrested for stalking and sending obscene content to a TV actress. He persisted with harassment across multiple profiles even after being blocked. The actress lured him to a meeting where she warned him, then alerted the police. He was taken into custody and faces charges under new criminal code sections.
title: 'Lured him to Cafe trap': Bengaluru man stalks TV actor, sends vulgar clips; arrested

author: TOI TECH DESK
description: India is rapidly emerging as GitHub's fastest-growing developer hub, projected to surpass the US in user numbers by 2030. The platform is strengthening its India-first strategy, supporting startups and student skilling.
title: 'AI won't replace coders': GitHub bets on AI-driven coding future; India leads developer growth

author: ASHISH CHAUHAN
title: How Gujarat hospital footage ended up on porn market
